            <p style="margin-top: 0.5rem; padding-left: 1rem;">Our <strong>guess the country game</strong> section offers multiple ways to test your geography skills. You can play <strong>guess country by shape</strong> to identify a nation purely by its map outline, or try <strong>guess country by flag</strong>. We even have regional challenges like <strong>guess the country Europe</strong>!</p>
